  {"id":"p3","nameEn":"Pork with Potatoes","name":"Sealiha kartulitega ahjus","cat":"Sealiha","thumb":"https://www.themealdb.com/images/media/meals/qtqvys1468573168.jpg","ingredients":[{"i":"Seakotletid","m":"4 tk"},{"i":"Kartul","m":"6 tk"},{"i":"Sibul","m":"2 tk"},{"i":"Porgand","m":"2 tk"},{"i":"Puljong","m":"200ml"},{"i":"Tüümian","m":"1 tl"},{"i":"Sool ja pipar","m":"maitse järgi"}],"steps":["Kuumuta ahi 190°C.","Lõika kartulid, sibul ja porgand tükkideks.","Aseta köögiviljad vormi, maitsesta.","Aseta kotletid peale, vala puljong.","Küpseta 50-60 min kuni kartulid on pehmed."]},
