  {"id":"p5","nameEn":"Pork Goulash","name":"Sealiha guljašš","cat":"Sealiha","thumb":"https://www.themealdb.com/images/media/meals/sqrtwu1511721265.jpg","ingredients":[{"i":"Sealiha","m":"600g"},{"i":"Sibul","m":"2 tk"},{"i":"Paprika","m":"2 tk"},{"i":"Tomatipasta","m":"2 sl"},{"i":"Paprikapulber","m":"2 tl"},{"i":"Lihapuljong","m":"400ml"},{"i":"Küüslauk","m":"2 küünt"},{"i":"Köömned","m":"1 tl"}],"steps":["Lõika liha 3cm kuubikuteks.","Pruunista liha õlis partiide kaupa.","Lisa sibul, paprika, küüslauk, prae 5 min.","Lisa paprikapulber ja tomatipasta.","Vala puljong, lisa köömned.","Hauta madalal kuumusel 60-70 min."]},
