  {"id":"pa1","nameEn":"Spaghetti Bolognese","name":"Spaghetti Bolognese","cat":"Pasta","thumb":"https://www.themealdb.com/images/media/meals/sutysw1468247559.jpg","ingredients":[{"i":"Spaghetti","m":"400g"},{"i":"Veise-seahakkliha","m":"500g"},{"i":"Purustatud tomatid","m":"400g"},{"i":"Sibul","m":"1 tk"},{"i":"Porgand","m":"1 tk"},{"i":"Küüslauk","m":"3 küünt"},{"i":"Punane vein","m":"100ml"},{"i":"Basiilik","m":"1 tl"},{"i":"Oliiviõli","m":"2 sl"},{"i":"Parmesaan","m":"50g"}],"steps":["Prae sibul, porgand, küüslauk oliiviõlis.","Lisa hakkliha, prae segades 10 min.","Vala vein, lase aurustuda.","Lisa purustatud tomatid, basiilik.","Hauta 30 min tasasel tulel.","Keeda spaghetti, sega kastmega.","Serveeri parmesaaniga."]},
